data.description: NEW LENNOX 3.5T HEAT PUMP SYSTEM  INSTALLED  6.08.21. 10 YR TRANSFERABLE WARRANTY TO NEW OWNER        Darling home located in a cul de sa street in Chapel Creek Ranch. Living area has a corner brick wood burning fireplace as a focal point.  Adjacent to LR  is area for separate dining. Large eat in kitchen with bay window, gas range, lots of counter space, cabinet storage & pantry. Spacious Master bedroom with dbl windows overlooking the backyd. Master bath provides separate shower, dbl sinks, garden tub & large walk-in closet. Plenty of room in backyard for kids to play. Being in popular Chapel Creek Ranch this house is convenient to I-30 and 820 for easy commuting.
